                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">being unable</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">We cannot pay the rent.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ma <hi rend="red">nǝgdar</hi> nǝdfaʕ l-īǧār.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wir können die Miete nicht zahlen.</cell>
                        <cell>لا نستطيع أن ندفع الأجرة.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">ability</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Can you (~do you know how to) play domino? – Yes.</cell>
